Thornwood Community Council have produced an analysis of the Streetwise 2023 Survey. 

"Do the numbers add up? In June 2023, Glasgow City Council commissioned Streetwise to undertake a parking survey in Thornwood and Broomhill.
We've taken a close look at those figures, and how they fit in with GCC's plans. 
Whether you're in favour of the RPZ or opposed to it, these figures raise questions that need to be answered."

You can read the full report here : https://www.thornwoodcc.org/latest-news/the-rpz/our-analysis
